    <IsekaiLeveling.SkillTree.PassiveTreeDef>
        <defName>PassiveTree_Survivor</defName>
        <label>Survivor</label>
        <treeClass>Survivor</treeClass>
        <treeDescription>Unbreakable souls who thrive where others perish. Five constellations radiate from the survivor's core — each forging a different link in their chain of endurance. When conditions worsen and mood drops, Unyielding Spirit kicks in to keep the Survivor alive against all odds.</treeDescription>
        <classGimmick>UnyieldingSpirit</classGimmick>
        <classGimmickName>Unyielding Spirit</classGimmickName>
        <classGimmickDescription>When the Survivor's mood drops below 50%, their body fights harder to stay alive. Immunity gain speed and rest effectiveness scale inversely with mood — the worse things get, the stronger the survival instinct. Unyielding Spirit scales along the Unyielding Path. Tier 1 (Never Yield): up to +20% at 0% mood. Tier 2 (Defiant Stand): up to +35%. Tier 3 (Last Stand): up to +55%. Tier 4 (Indomitable Will): up to +80%. The darkness fuels the will to survive.</classGimmickDescription>

